# Documentation

- Update README when project structure or setup changes.
- Public API gets brief JSDoc on exports; private code does not.
- No comment noise; names and structure carry meaning.
- Phase completion includes a doc pass (see `project/docs` skill).
- Code explains itself first — refactor instead of commenting.

Load `.cursor/skills/project/docs/SKILL.md` when completing a phase or adding public API.
